The,Apitude,Booking,API,provides,developers,a,way,to,access,to,all,hotelbeds,prices,and,availabilities,as,they,are,in,an,specific,moment,in,time,so,that,they,can,be,used,for,package,travel,or,upload,it,to,third,party,platforms,The,API,enables,users,to,manage,the,entire,hotel,booking,process,Hotelbeds,is,a,travel,agency,based,in,Spain,which,provides,a,global,hotel,database,for,B,B,partners